lyrics:
[Verse]
My place is back on the level, back on the level
No longer feeling downtrodden and unsettled
I walk with confidence, nothing to prove
Leaving behind the cruel and unusual

[Chorus]
Back on the level, back on the level
Rising above the doubts, feeling invincible
My spirit soars high, with a newfound grace
Leaving behind the shadows, embracing a better space
